  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Comparison between fetal MRI and fetal echocardiography</measure>
    <time_frame>within 2 weeks of participation in the study</time_frame>
    <description>Anatomic MR images of the fetal heart will be acquired using prospective gating information from the Doppler ultrasound probe (SMART-SYNC LM03) and used to calculate ejection fraction. These values will be compared with corresponding reference values obtained during the patient's visit to the Fetal Echocardiography Clinic.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
