      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  pregnant adults (age 18 and up) with fetus affected by congenital heart disease&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  singleton pregnancy in their 2nd and 3rd trimesters&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  scheduled for a clinical fetal ultrasound examination at the Fetal Echocardiography&#xD;
             Clinic at SickKids&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  claustrophobia&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  cardiac pacemaker&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  non-MRI compatible implants&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  non-singleton pregnancy&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  obesity (BMI &gt; 30)&#xD;
      </textblock>
